    <item>
      <title>布林肯访华前夕，中国谴责美国产能过剩的说法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-condemns-us-s-overcapacity-claim-just-before-blinken-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对美国对工业产能过剩的抱怨发起了迄今为止最严厉的攻击，这表明国务卿安东尼·布林肯在本周访问期间可能会进行一些艰难的对话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-condemns-us-s-overcapacity-claim-just-before-blinken-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:50:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在卢旺达移民计划惨败后面临法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/sunak-s-rwanda-deportation-bill-to-become-law-after-long-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理里希·苏纳克在一场暴露了保守党内部深刻分歧的斗争中确保通过具有里程碑意义的移民立法后，发誓要克服进一步的挑战，并继续推进飞往卢旺达的驱逐航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/sunak-s-rwanda-deportation-bill-to-become-law-after-long-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 23:21:30 GMT</pubDate>
